[I] UTF-8 with C++ in a Portable Way

[T] A small, C++98 compatible generic library in order to handle UTF-8
[T] encoded strings. For anybody used to work with STL algorithms and
[T] iterators, it should be easy and natural to use.

[U] https://github.com/nemtrif/utfcpp

